# apps/backend/src/modules/message/

## Responsibility
Creates, updates, fetches, and soft-deletes conversation messages.

## Design
Idempotent send path via uniqueTempId, status history tracking, and queue-driven outbound delivery for agent/bot messages.

## Flow
Send writes message rows, links media, updates conversation last-message/unread state, and enqueues outbound processing when applicable.

## Integration
Relies on Prisma and outboundMessageQueue; updates feed conversation timelines and external channel delivery workers.

